p: Territory of Washington, County of Spokane}ss To the Sheriff of Spokane County Greeting: In the name of the United States, You are hereby commanded to apprehend and bring the Hon. George Turner Judge of the District Court of the Territory of Washington, and for the Fourth Judicial District thereof, the body John Mabius to show cause, if there be any, why did not obey his recognizance heretofore given to be and appear at the District Court holding terms at the county seal of Spokane County to the 3rd monday in November A.D. 1886. D.A. Clement Clerk By Deputy.
